Instructions for treasure hunt -

1. Time to complete is 45 mins, max is a 15 mins buffer, we will be breaking for lunch at 12 and back at Princeton at 1pm for the post lunch activities 

2. Maintain the same team throughout the game, any swapping of team members will lead to disqualification 

3. Make sure to register yourself and your team at each clue spot and take a team selfie at the same place 

4. Team with maximum solved clues in the least time will be chosen the winner 

5. Tower 2 is out of bounds, clues can be anywhere around the campus, but tower 2.

6. None of the clue spots require your badge access 

7. There's just one winner in this treasure hunt, so may the best team win

Please contact us at +91 9686662439 for any queries
